{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"iddcd4a4fb-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06","identifier":"/us/usc/t12/s2277a–5"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2277a–5"},"text":"§ 2277a–5.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Certification of premiums","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"iddcd4a4fc-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06","identifier":"/us/usc/t12/s2277a–5/a"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"a"},"text":"(a)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Filing certified statement","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":"On a date to be determined in the sole discretion of the Board of Directors of the Corporation, each insured System bank that became insured before the beginning of the period for which premiums are being assessed (referred to in this section as the “period”) shall file with the Corporation a certified statement showing—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"iddcd4a4fd-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06","identifier":"/us/usc/t12/s2277a–5/a/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" the average outstanding insured obligations for the period issued by the bank;","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"iddcd4a4fe-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06","identifier":"/us/usc/t12/s2277a–5/a/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"iddcd4a4ff-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06","identifier":"/us/usc/t12/s2277a–5/a/2/A"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"A"},"text":"(A)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" the average principal outstanding for the period on the guaranteed portion of Federal government-guaranteed loans that are in accrual status; and","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"iddcd4a500-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06","identifier":"/us/usc/t12/s2277a–5/a/2/B"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"B"},"text":"(B)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" the average amount outstanding for the period of Federal government-guaranteed investments that are not permanently impaired (as defined in ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t12/s2277a–4/a/4"},"text":"section 2277a–4(a)(4) of this title","children":[],"tail":");"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"iddcd4a501-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06","identifier":"/us/usc/t12/s2277a–5/a/3"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"3"},"text":"(3)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"iddcd4a502-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06","identifier":"/us/usc/t12/s2277a–5/a/3/A"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"A"},"text":"(A)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" the average principal outstanding for the period on State government-guaranteed loans that are in accrual status; and","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"iddcd4a503-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06","identifier":"/us/usc/t12/s2277a–5/a/3/B"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"B"},"text":"(B)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" the average amount outstanding for the period of State government-guaranteed investments that are not permanently impaired (as defined in ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t12/s2277a–4/a/4"},"text":"section 2277a–4(a)(4) of this title","children":[],"tail":");"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"iddcd4a504-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06","identifier":"/us/usc/t12/s2277a–5/a/4"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"4"},"text":"(4)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"iddcd4a505-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06","identifier":"/us/usc/t12/s2277a–5/a/4/A"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"A"},"text":"(A)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" the average principal outstanding for the period on loans that are in nonaccrual status; and","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"iddcd4a506-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06","identifier":"/us/usc/t12/s2277a–5/a/4/B"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"B"},"text":"(B)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" the average amount outstanding for the period of other-than-temporarily impaired investments; and","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"iddcd4a507-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06","identifier":"/us/usc/t12/s2277a–5/a/5"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"5"},"text":"(5)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" the amount of the premium due the Corporation from the bank for the period.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"iddcd4a508-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06","identifier":"/us/usc/t12/s2277a–5/b"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"b"},"text":"(b)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Contents and form of statement","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The certified statement required to be filed with the Corporation under subsection (a) shall be in such form and set forth such supporting information as the Board of Directors shall prescribe, and shall be certified by the president of the bank or any other officer designated by its board of directors that to the best of the person’s knowledge and belief the statement is true, correct, complete, and has been prepared in accordance with this part and all regulations issued thereunder.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"iddcd4a509-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06","identifier":"/us/usc/t12/s2277a–5/c"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"c"},"text":"(c)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Premium payments","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"iddcd4a50a-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06","identifier":"/us/usc/t12/s2277a–5/c/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" In general","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Except as provided in paragraph (2), each insured System bank shall pay to the Corporation the premium payments required under subsection (a), not more frequently than once in each calendar quarter, in such manner and at such 1 or more times as the Board of Directors shall prescribe.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"iddcd4a50b-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06","identifier":"/us/usc/t12/s2277a–5/c/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Premium amount","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The amount of the premium shall be established not later than 60 days after filing the certified statement specifying the amount of the premium.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"iddcd4a50c-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06","identifier":"/us/usc/t12/s2277a–5/d"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"d"},"text":"(d)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Regulations","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The Board of Directors shall prescribe all rules and regulations necessary for the enforcement of this section. The Board of Directors may limit the retroactive effect, if any, of any of its rules or regulations.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"iddcd4a50d-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/92/181/tV/s5"},"text":"Pub. L. 92–181, title V, § 5","children":[],"tail":".56, as added "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/100/233/tIII/s302"},"text":"Pub. L. 100–233, title III, § 302","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1988-01-06"},"text":"Jan. 6, 1988","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/101/1612"},"text":"101 Stat. 1612","children":[],"tail":"; amended "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/100/399/tIII/s302/f"},"text":"Pub. L. 100–399, title III, § 302(f)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1988-08-17"},"text":"Aug. 17, 1988","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/102/994"},"text":"102 Stat. 994","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/101/624/tXVIII/s1835"},"text":"Pub. L. 101–624, title XVIII, § 1835","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1990-11-28"},"text":"Nov. 28, 1990","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/104/3833"},"text":"104 Stat. 3833","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/104/105/tII/s215/a/2/B"},"text":"Pub. L. 104–105, title II, § 215(a)(2)(B)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1996-02-10"},"text":"Feb. 10, 1996","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/110/176"},"text":"110 Stat. 176","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/107/171/tV/s5403/a/2/B"},"text":"Pub. L. 107–171, title V, § 5403(a)(2)(B)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2002-05-13"},"text":"May 13, 2002","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/116/351"},"text":"116 Stat. 351","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/110/234/tV/s5405"},"text":"Pub. L. 110–234, title V, § 5405","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2008-05-22"},"text":"May 22, 2008","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/122/1157"},"text":"122 Stat. 1157","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/110/246/s4/a"},"text":"Pub. L. 110–246, § 4(a)","children":[],"tail":", title V, § 5405, "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2008-06-18"},"text":"June 18, 2008","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/122/1664"},"text":"122 Stat. 1664","children":[],"tail":", 1919.)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"iddcd4a50e-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"iddcd4a50f-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"codification","id":"iddcd4a510-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Codification","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/110/234"},"text":"Pub. L. 110–234","children":[],"tail":" and "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/110/246"},"text":"Pub. L. 110–246","children":[],"tail":" made identical amendments to this section. The amendments by "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/110/234"},"text":"Pub. L. 110–234","children":[],"tail":" were repealed by "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/110/246/s4/a"},"text":"section 4(a) of Pub. L. 110–246","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"amendments","id":"iddcd4a511-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Amendments","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"2008—Subsec. (a). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/110/246/s5405/a"},"text":"Pub. L. 110–246, § 5405(a)","children":[],"tail":", added subsec. (a) and struck out former subsec. (a) which related to the required annual filing of a certified statement from each insured System bank that became insured before the beginning of the year."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsec. (c). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/110/246/s5405/b"},"text":"Pub. L. 110–246, § 5405(b)","children":[],"tail":", added subsec. (c) and struck out former subsec. (c). Prior to amendment, text read as follows: “Each System bank shall pay to the Corporation the amount of the initial premium it is required to certify under subsection (a) of this section as soon as practicable after "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1990-01-01"},"text":"January 1, 1990","children":[],"tail":", based on the application of "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t12/s2277a–4"},"text":"section 2277a–4 of this title","children":[],"tail":" to the accruing loan volume of the bank for calendar year 1989.”"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsecs. (d), (e). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/110/246/s5405/c"},"text":"Pub. L. 110–246, § 5405(c)","children":[],"tail":", redesignated subsec. (e) as (d) and struck out former subsec. (d). Prior to amendment, text read as follows: “The premium payments required from insured System banks under subsection (a) of this section shall be made not less frequently than annually in such manner and at such time or times as the Board of Directors shall prescribe, except that the amount of the premium shall be established not later than 60 days after filing the certified statement setting forth the amount of the premium.”"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"2002—Subsec. (a)(1). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/107/171/s5403/a/2/B/i"},"text":"Pub. L. 107–171, § 5403(a)(2)(B)(i)","children":[],"tail":", inserted “and Government Sponsored Enterprise-guaranteed loans (as defined in "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t12/s2277a–4/a/4"},"text":"section 2277a–4(a)(4) of this title","children":[],"tail":")” after “government-guaranteed loans”."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsec. (a)(4) to (6). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/107/171/s5403/a/2/B/ii"},"text":"Pub. L. 107–171, § 5403(a)(2)(B)(ii)","children":[],"tail":", (iii), added par. (4) and redesignated former pars. (4) and (5) as (5) and (6), respectively."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1996—Subsec. (a)(2), (3). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/104/105"},"text":"Pub. L. 104–105","children":[],"tail":" substituted “2277a–4(a)(3) of this title” for “2277a–4(a)(2) of this title”."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1990—Subsec. (a). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/101/624"},"text":"Pub. L. 101–624","children":[],"tail":" amended subsec. (a) generally. Prior to amendment, subsec. (a) read as follows: “Annually, on a date to be determined in the sole discretion of the Board of Directors, each insured System bank that became insured before the beginning of the year shall file with the Corporation a certified statement showing the annual average principal outstanding on loans made by the bank that are in accrual status, the annual average principal outstanding on loans that are in nonaccrual status, and the amount of the premium due the Corporation from the bank for such year.”"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1988—Subsec. (a). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/100/399"},"text":"Pub. L. 100–399","children":[],"tail":" substituted “of the year” for “of such year”."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"statutoryNotes","id":"iddcd4a512-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"effectiveDateOfAmendment","id":"iddcd4a513-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Effective Date of 2008 Amendment","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Amendment of this section and repeal of ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/110/234"},"text":"Pub. L. 110–234","children":[],"tail":" by "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/110/246"},"text":"Pub. L. 110–246","children":[],"tail":" effective "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2008-05-22"},"text":"May 22, 2008","children":[],"tail":", the date of enactment of "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/110/234"},"text":"Pub. L. 110–234","children":[],"tail":", see "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/110/246/s4"},"text":"section 4 of Pub. L. 110–246","children":[],"tail":", set out as an Effective Date note under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t7/s8701"},"text":"section 8701 of Title 7","children":[],"tail":", Agriculture."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"effectiveDateOfAmendment","id":"iddcd4a514-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Effective Date of 2002 Amendment","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Amendment by ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/107/171"},"text":"Pub. L. 107–171","children":[],"tail":" applicable with respect to determinations of premiums for calendar year 2002 and for any succeeding calendar year, and to certified statements with respect to such premiums, see "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/107/171/s5403/b"},"text":"section 5403(b) of Pub. L. 107–171","children":[],"tail":", set out as a note under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t12/s2020"},"text":"section 2020 of this title","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"effectiveDateOfAmendment","id":"iddcd4a515-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Effective Date of 1988 Amendment","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Amendment by ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/100/399"},"text":"Pub. L. 100–399","children":[],"tail":" effective as if enacted immediately after enactment of "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/100/233"},"text":"Pub. L. 100–233","children":[],"tail":", which was approved "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1988-01-06"},"text":"Jan. 6, 1988","children":[],"tail":", see "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/100/399/s1001/a"},"text":"section 1001(a) of Pub. L. 100–399","children":[],"tail":", set out as a note under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t12/s2002"},"text":"section 2002 of this title","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
